Theme:         LETTERS DEPARTMENT


features:
there are two bulletin boards (more to come) for players
willing to write their own notes on specific subjects.

rooms:
there are 7 rooms, eventually expandable in the future.

mobs:
there is one big monster (a full professor) which is helped
by several ushers when is attacked.

items:
a golden watch (treasure).
a walking cane (weapon).
the items are not of obvious use.

thanks

fran



completed June 23rd 2001
revised July 12th 2001

